# Title: Modification of IE Registry Settings
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-01-22
# Level: low
# Description: Detects modification of the registry settings used for Internet Explorer and other Windows components that use these settings. An attacker can abuse this registry key to add a domain to the trusted sites Zone or insert JavaScript for persistence
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1112

TargetObject="*\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Internet Settings*" NOT (Details="Binary Data" OR Details="DWORD*" OR NOT Details=* OR Details IN ("Cookie:", "Visited:", "(Empty)") OR TargetObject IN ("*\\Cache*", "*\\ZoneMap*", "*\\WpadDecision*")) NOT TargetObject="*\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Internet Settings\\Accepted Documents*"